tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_activity (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id UUID,
    action_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    tool_used VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE user_activity (
    user_id INT,
    activity_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    activity_description STRING,
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id, activity_id)
);

CREATE TABLE user_interaction (
    interaction_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_type STRING,
    interaction_details STRING,
    PRIMARY KEY (interaction_id)
);

CREATE TABLE user_interaction (
    interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_details JSONB,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES user_activity(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE whiteboard_data (
    board_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    board_name VARCHAR(100),
    created_by UUID,
    created_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    last_updated_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    board_data JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    duration INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE activities (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    session_id INT,
    activity_type VARCHAR(50),
    activity_data JSONB,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    session_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_data JSONB,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE UserActivity (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    activity_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    duration INT
)

CREATE TABLE WhiteboardInteractions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    whiteboard_id INT,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE UserAccounts (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(50),
    account_created_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE WhiteboardData (
    whiteboard_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    title VARCHAR(100),
    owner_id INT,
    created_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE UserSession (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP
)
